0.5.6 / 2025-04-13

	* Accept writer or reader in place of index for more efficient
	bulk operations.
	* Support metadata on :_content default field
	* Support :include metadata for :_content, specifying fields to
	include in default field
	* Add tests for fields metadata, including defalut field
	* Document writer/reader option and :_content metadata in README
	* Document some Lucene gotchas in README

0.5.5 / 2025-04-12

	* Expand acceptabe types for dir arg in `disk-index`.
	
	* Fix incorrect meta field name in README.

0.5.4 / 2025-04-10

	* Add convenience fn for making per-field analyzer
	
	* Fix bug setting :indexed in meta of returned document maps.
	
	* Improvements to README.
	
	* Improvements to docstrings.


0.5.3 / 2025-04-01

	* Fix bug ignoring :indexed field option.
	
	* Add minimum Clojure version to README.
	
	* Simplify code.
	
	* Improve README formatting.

0.5.2 / 2025-03-31

	* Fix README "project.clj"->"deps.edn"

0.5.1 / 2025-03-31

	* Update ChangeLog
	
	* Update README

0.5.0 / 2025-03-31

	* Support for Lucene 10.1.0
	
	* Migrate to tools.deps (deps.edn, removing project.clj)
	
	* Eliminate reflection
	
	* Fork, changing name to Clucille
	
	* Move into com.ryantate ns
	
	* Linting, various, including idiomatic use of `require`

0.3.0 / 2012-04-10

	* Support for Lucene 3.5.0

0.2.2 / 2011-07-03

	* Support versions of Lucene other than 3.0.

0.2.1 / 2011-05-31

	* Expose score, total hits, and max-score metadata.

	* Allow for result highlighting.

0.2.0 / 2011-05-04

	* Add deletion functionality.

	* Accept per-field store/index settings.

0.1.0 / 2010-03-26

	* Initial release.
